title: Wrangell - St Elias National Park & Preserve: Watersheds
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Nature     Natural Features & Ecosystems     Watersheds                Watersheds       There are two major watersheds within the boundaries of Wrangell-St. Elias: the Copper River drainage which drains into the Gulf of Alaska and the Yukon River drainage which empties into the Bering Sea.
